title: Grateful Dead Live at Capital Centre on 1993-03-16
description:
Set 1

Jack Straw, Row Jimmy, Minglewood Blues, So Many Roads, Cassidy, Tennessee Jed, Promised Land

Set 2

Scarlet Begonias-> Fire On The Mountain, Women Are Smarter, Uncle John's Band-> Jam*-> Drums-> Jam-> The Last Time-> Morning Dew-> Sugar Magnolia, E: U.S. Blues

*w/o Jerry and Bobby major Phil Jamming

reviews.review_text: 03-16-1993 Great second set into drums landover was the best 1971-1994 longest venue ever for the dead period
